node.text:
🔉#SOUNDON: We’re going green for our #digestion 💚😍 Treat your #gut with this Garden Greens Soup! The leafy greens in it are a good source of #fiber, that can help the growth of #healthy gut #bacteria. 
Full Recipe: 
1 bunch kale (8-10 whole leaves)
3 ½ cups chicken or vegetable broth
½ bunch fresh parsley, leaves only, coarsely chopped (about 1 cup, loosely packed)
3 cups fresh spinach leaves (about 3 ounces)
2 cups broccoli florets (about 5 ounces)
1 large carrot, coarsely grated
3 green onions (both white and green parts), roughly chopped
2 large garlic cloves, roughly chopped
2 TBSP white miso paste, or to taste
Juice of half a lemon, or to taste
1/4 TSP red pepper flakes
Salt and pepper to taste
4 scoops Herbalife Nutrition Simply Probiotic

Per serving:
Calories:  160
Protein: 13 g
Carbohydrate: 27 g
Fat: 3 g
Fiber: 6.5 g

🍊 Vitamin C: citrus fruits, peppers, broccoli, & kale

node.text:
Celebrate #PiñaColadaDay with this Aloe Colada Protein Shake! #LoveMyShake 

Combine in blender:
1 cup water
2 scoops Herbalife Nutrition Formula 1 Shake Mix, Piña Colada*
2 TBSP Personalized Protein Powder
3 capfuls Herbal Aloe Concentrate, Mango
1/2 cup pineapple chunks 
3-5 ice cubes

Blend to mix well.

180 calories 
25 G protein 

#HerbalifeNutrition 
*Available in the US and Puerto Rico

node.text:
#WorldChocolateDay calls for these #vegan treats! 🍫

Ingredients:
•2 cups mashed overripe bananas (about 6 medium)
•1 cup crunchy peanut butter (use almond or cashew butter for paleo/low-carb)
•1/2 cup (67g) Herbalife Nutrition Tri Blend Select Coffee Caramel*
•1/4 cup cocoa 

Instructions: 
1. Pre-heat oven to 375° F / 190° C. Line a small 8x8 oven tray or 8’’ skillet grease well. Set aside.
2. In a large bowl, combine the mashed bananas, peanut butter, whisk until fully combined. Stir in Tri Blend Select and cocoa powder with a wooden spoon.
3. Pour batter into a greased pan. Bake for 25 minutes or until cooked through.
4. Cool for at least 15 minutes before cutting. Cover the leftovers and store in the fridge for up to 3 days.
5. Enjoy cold or at room temperature.

272 calories | 11 g protein per piece 
Vegan, Gluten Free & Paleo | Serves: 9

*Available in select markets in Europe, and Australia/New Zealand

@herbalifeuk @herbalifeanz 

Only when prepared as instructed on the product label does our product deliver the full nutrition benefits described on that label. Please remember that if a Herbalife Nutrition product is used in a heated recipe, some vitamin levels in the finished product may decline in comparison to label values.
